description.from:
Enumerated list of price rounding types.
        ENUM: ['NearestDown', 'NearestUp', 'Par', 'ParAndStack']. Rounding options to target a par price.
        NearestDown rounds nearest price above Par down to achieve Par
        NearestUp round nearest price below par up to achieve Par
        Par rounds nearest price to par up or down to achieve par
        ParStack allows users to configure specific range of prices and round each either to par or by same amount to get nearest to par.

        ENUM: ['Nearest', 'NearestDown', 'NearestUp', 'Par', 'ParAndStack']. Rounding options to target a par price.
        Nearest rounds to nearest price to par
        NearestDown rounds nearest price above Par down to achieve Par
        NearestUp round nearest price below par up to achieve Par
        Par rounds nearest price to par up or down to achieve par
        ParStack allows users to configure specific range of prices and round each either to par or by same amount to get nearest to par.

* `NearestDown` - NearestDown
* `NearestUp` - NearestUp
* `Par` - Par
* `ParAndStack` - ParAndStack
* `ParAndRange` - ParAndRange
